6 weeks before my colonoscopy - I'd been having stomach issues and my GP ordered a CT, it was normal so I went to a GI doc. #coloncancer
4 weeks before my colonoscopy - GI doc looked at CT, did exam & ordered colonoscopy to 'explore.'  I knew this was an option. #coloncancer
2 weeks before my colonoscopy - The hospital called to go over my meds and talk me through the procedure, what to expect, etc. #coloncancer
2 days before my colonoscopy - No raw veg or fruit to eat & no nuts.  I filled my MoviPrep scrip. #coloncancer http://t.co/oGGlFv84ZJ
1 day before my colonoscopy - The fun starts:) I am on a clear liquid diet for 24 hours and I start MoviPrep at 5 pm. #coloncancer
1 day before my colonoscopy - People led me to believe that this would happen ... it did not. #coloncancer http://t.co/H9SyDKniwA
1 day before my colonoscopy - After MoviPrep I needed to go to the bathroom. It was not sudden & a stomach flu is far worse. #coloncancer
